sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant React as React Frontend
    participant Main as Main Server
    participant Cache as Main Cache
    participant DB as Main SQLite
    participant Worker as Worker Node

    React->>Main: POST /API/V1/Auth/SignIn (email, password)
    Main->>DB: Verify hash, load User
    Main->>Main: Check Has2FAEnabled
    alt 2FA on
        Main-->>React: 200 { Step: AwaitTotp, ChallengeId }
        React->>Main: POST /API/V1/Auth/Verify2FA (totp, ChallengeId)
        Main->>Main: Validate TOTP
    end
    Main->>Cache: GET MainWorker:Company:{id}:WorkerNodeId
    alt cache hit
        Cache-->>Main: WorkerNodeId
    else cache miss
        Main->>DB: SELECT WorkerNodeId FROM Company
        DB-->>Main: WorkerNodeId
        Main->>Cache: SET (TTL 15m)
    end
    Main->>Main: Mint RS256 worker JWT (sub, cmp, wnk, aud, exp, roles)
    Main-->>React: 200 { WorkerEndpoint, WorkerJwt, JwtExpiresAt }

    Note over React,Worker: All subsequent business calls bypass Main
    React->>Worker: GET /API/V1/Company/{slug} (Authorization: Bearer JWT)
    Worker->>Worker: Validate signature, exp, aud, wnk, cmp claims
    Worker-->>React: 200 (data)

    Note over React,Main: Token refresh near expiry
    React->>Main: POST /API/V1/Auth/RefreshWorkerToken
    Main-->>React: 200 { WorkerJwt, JwtExpiresAt }
